## Implementation Steps

1. Create handlers/registry.rs
2. Implement render() for full capability display
3. Implement render_summary() for compact view
4. Add section headers and footers
5. Integrate all three sub-renderers
6. Add Server::display_capabilities() method
7. Implement plain-text fallback
8. Test with various capability combinations

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Full render shows all capability types
- [ ] Summary provides quick overview
- [ ] Empty sections are hidden gracefully
- [ ] Section ordering is consistent
- [ ] Totals are calculated correctly
- [ ] Plain-text fallback works
- [ ] Integrates with Server struct

